[Travi to Ropa]

Goal: 
To have a Margarita cocktail prepared in the mixing_container, shaked with the electric_shaker and then poured into first_glass placed on the tray.

Object needed: 
electric_shaker, mixing_container, first_glass, ice_cubes, tequila_bottle, triple_sec_bottle, lime_slice, tray 

State summary from environment state: 
The robot currently has nothing in its hands. The bottles of tequila and triple sec are on the shelf, the lime slice and ice cubes are already in the mixing container. The tray, first_glass, electric_shaker and the mixing_container are on the table. 

Remaining actions to do: 
Since the mixing_container has already been filled with the ingredients, they can't be closed because it isn't closeable. To continue, you can proceed as follows:
- switch on the electric_shaker;
- wait until the shaking process is done (assuming it would take 15 seconds);
- switch off the electric_shaker;
- get first_glass with your left hand;
- pour the souled mixing_container into first_glass;
- put first_glass on the tray.
